Andre Gignac says he made the 'stunning discovery' in a photograph released by Nasa and taken by the Mars rover Opportunity . 
  He claims to have spotted what he believes to be a bunker on the red planet with armed people peering out of its windows . 
  He says he also spotted missiles, rockets and structures in the image . 
  The discovery follows a spate of strange objects found on Mars . 
  Last year a UFO hunter spotted a 'coffin' on the planet . 
  Other objects found in images of Mars include fossilised lizards . 
 